Biography 
Real name - Ekaterina Kozlova. 
05-27-1993, St. Petersburg. 
The girl has a younger brother. 
The range of creative interests of Ekaterina Rys is wide - from literature to the modeling business, cinema and the art of photography. From the age of 15, the girl worked as a model. As a writer, Kozlova dabbled in poetry and prose. Under the pseudonym Lolita Oxel, she published her literary experiences on thematic websites of the Russian Internet. Stellar career In the early 2010s, Kozlova became famous as an actress of erotic films. Ekaterina Rys is just one of the many creative pseudonyms of the artist. Fans of the cinema category 18+ also know her under the names Monroe, Sweet Monroe, Blond Angel, Lolita Monroe, Katerina Kozlova. 
In the porn industry, Ekaterina Rys has a screen image of an innocent, but extremely seductive young nymphet. In films, the artist does not enter into intimate relationships with men. She is engaged in self-satisfaction on camera, successfully bringing the audience to the necessary condition. The corporate image of Ekaterina Rys has gained great popularity among fans of candid film production. The secret of the artist's success was due to her external data. Blond hair, a naive look and round cheeks formed the reference image of a young angel. They allowed the girl to look significantly younger than her age. An impressive bust and expressive roundness did not leave the audience a chance to resist the beauty of the beauty.

posts.subject: OF Poem 09-2021
posts.body:
When you are ready, I will surrender
Take me and do as you will
Have what you want, your way's always the best way
I have succumbed to this passive sensation
Peacefully falling away
I am the zombie, your wish will command me
Laugh as I fall to my knees
Can I control this empty delusion?
Lost in the fire below
And you come running your eyes will be open
And when you come back, I'll be as you want me
Only so eager to please
My little song will keep you beside me
Thinking your name as I sing
